cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper involves machine learning techniques applied to robotics control, specifically inverse dynamics learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves robotics and control, which suggests the categories cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as likely options. Additionally, the paper involves state-dependent loss functions, which suggests the categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as possible options, as these fields often involve state-dependent modeling and optimization.
